  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version: `Version: 1.6.6-stable`\r\nOS & Version: Ubuntu 16.04.2 LTS\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\nPassing invalid nonce in the sendTransaction should return false or invalid transaction\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\nTransaction ID is generated and returned to the caller - yet the transaction will disappear from txpool.content.pending, txpool.content.queued and from getTransaction after a few minutes.\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\nSend a transaction with a nonce higher than what getTransactionCount(address) returns",
